title: Smack - On You - 1984 - Finnish rock, Hanoi Rocks, Stooges, MC5.
description:
Smack - an excellent Finnish rock band in the style of the Stooges, Dead Boys, Hanoi Rocks, Backyard Babies, Sex Pistols and MC5.

This CD features their original 1984 album plus some bonus cuts.

1. Good Morning Headache 
  2. Run Rabbit Run 
  3. Through The Glass 
  4. Skin Alley 
  5. Little C**t 
  6. Completely Alone 
  7. Some Fun 
  8. Ten Foot Cell 
  9. Primitive 
  10. Cemetary Walls 
  11. Criminal 
  12. No Peace On Earth 
  13. Criminal - (Bonus Track) 
  14. Little C**t - (Bonus Track) 
  15. Walkin On The Wire - (Bonus Track) 
  16. Blank - (Bonus Track) 
  17. I Wanna Be Your Dog - (Bonus Track) 


Enjoy!
